{"tid":1346526,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急呼籲]請各個界別人工立即在TG成立網上工會","createTime":"2019-07-22T04:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T20:43:03.000Z","uid":1915,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"58c1eecef5a18a6689b1a1837ac350d630d368b8","tid":1346526,"uid":1915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:21:33.000Z","msg":"我認為香港有急切需要所有界別都成立工會以對抗暴政！<br />\n有見香港各個界別勞工都近乎沒有工會，<span style=\"color: red;\">難以有效及有組織地發動任何運動及保護自己既權益</span>，即使要發動罷工都<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有渠道得到共識及相關資訊</span>。<br />\n<br />\n香港表面上係可以自由成立工會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/labour/content3_1.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Flabour%2Fcontent3_1.htm&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIPLVWyXx0XMfrvcdwhNvS5Y%3D&h=829d9d6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/labour/content3_1.htm</a><br />\n但實際上當權者及既得利益者在資本主義及極權之下打壓一般市民，所以各界只有極少有效且有籌碼既工會。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">成立TG工會，可以保持無大台、be water既原則，令暴政難以打擊。</span><br />\n<br />\n利申番緊工不能長時間芒住，希望各位有心之士接力推動，集思廣益<br />\n各有各做！不割不分！"},{"pid":"f4d40a7ed434a551ae2fec1b42fb4c9d6783df61","tid":1346526,"uid":1915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:43:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e5415dceb1d3a082ee3ea03bd3dd7c6179faf5f","tid":1346526,"uid":1915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:59:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a27e46038f25126c40d1c543c9909609ec2d56da","tid":1346526,"uid":283157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:00:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbfb6fec6545cfa9cee76de271770e38f9f948be","tid":1346526,"uid":1915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:05:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e31cea0b8f588b0e2cf7a3c39b9f7531b134347","tid":1346526,"uid":283157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:38:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88cb083f8c163fdc9b45ecaffa999ff1fb24af3